
It is also possible to apply document discounts from Related-> Order->Detailed Discounts:

<img width="" src="https://docs-test.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000420-0/Detailed Document Discounts - Usage_Document Discount Header_ENU_001.png"><br>

There is a table like the previous one in which to enter the discounts.

Header discounts can be inherited from:
* **Payment terms**
* **Shipping methods**

 On both pages there is the "Detailed Discount" field where the discounts are entered.


<img width="" src="https://docs-test.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000420-0/Detailed Document Discounts - Usage_Document Discount Header_ENU_002.png"><br>

